234
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:02,860
So what?

235
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,380
My sister is

236
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,440
ten times smarter than me.

237
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,420
She is always right.

238
00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:10,620
The more obedient you are,

239
00:12:10,740 --> 00:12:12,020
