240
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,860
My sister wouldn't think less of me.

241
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:16,340
Right?

242
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:20,700
She's your sister.

243
00:12:21,020 --> 00:12:22,220
