244
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,020
Your playful friends

245
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:25,100
won't be of any help.

246
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:26,500
Are you trying

247
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:27,820
to go out and have fun again?

248
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:31,580
As long as I pass the selection

249
