00:31:05,500 --> 00:31:06,340
Mother.

585
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:08,340
What exactly happened last night?

586
00:31:09,500 --> 00:31:10,900
Tell me everything.

587
00:31:11,180 --> 00:31:12,540
Don't miss anything.

588
00:31:14,060 --> 00:31:17,060
(Duke An's Mansion)

589
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:20,140
Be gentle.

590
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:23,660
Son, bear with it.

591
00:31:30,420 --> 00:31:31,260
Physician,

592
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:32,820
how is

593
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,940
my son's leg injury?

594
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:34,780
Ma'am,

595
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:36,900
his leg is severely injured.

596
00:31:37,300 --> 00:31:38,180
I'm afraid

597
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:39,820
he won't be able to walk again.

598
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:41,780
He's still so young.

599
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:43,100
He can't be crippled.

600
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,300
Whatever it costs,

601
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:45,540
we must cure him.

602
00:31:46,460 --> 00:31:48,740
You should seek a better physician.

603
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:51,300
- Physician...
- You...

604
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:53,420
Please treat my leg.

605
00:31:53,420 --> 00:31:54,260
Mother.

606
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:56,500
Physician, please think of something.

607
00:31:56,980 --> 00:31:57,820
Physician...

608
00:31:58,020 --> 00:32:00,580
- Mother, save my leg.
- Physician, save my son.

609
00:32:01,020 --> 00:32:01,860
Physician...

610
00:32:08,900 --> 00:32:09,740
Ji Chongyi,

611
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:11,780
if you harm my baby,

612
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:13,020
I will not let this go.

613
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:14,540
I'm hurt,

614
00:32:14,740 --> 00:32:16,660
