615
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:18,820
How can you be so cruel?

616
00:32:19,020 --> 00:32:20,420
I'm cruel?

617
00:32:21,820 --> 00:32:22,660
Ji Chongyi,

618
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:25,660
you're just a tool I used
to get into this family.

619
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:28,100
Whether you're crippled or not,

620
00:32:29,100 --> 00:32:30,180
I couldn't care less.

621
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:33,340
You venous woman.

622
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,540
I told you

623
00:32:37,060 --> 00:32:39,580
Princess Mingyue was overbearing.

624
00:32:40,340 --> 00:32:42,500
Everyone in Ling'an was avoiding her,

625
00:32:43,060 --> 00:32:44,340
yet you still tried to get close.

626
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:45,180
Look.

627
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:47,060
Look at you now.

628
00:32:47,060 --> 00:32:48,620
What do you know as a businesswoman?

629
00:32:48,740 --> 00:32:50,020
I'm doing all this

630
00:32:50,020 --> 00:32:52,180
for the future of our family.

631
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:54,820
The Grand Princess holds power now.

632
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,100
Can I afford to offend her?

633
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:59,660
The court is full of intrigue.

634
00:33:00,700 --> 00:33:02,100
Even your father can't handle it.

635
00:33:02,580 --> 00:33:03,740
Who do you think you are

636
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:04,620
to get involved?

637
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,540
You're just seeking death.

638
00:33:08,300 --> 00:33:09,180
If not for worrying

639
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:10,260
about my baby,

640
00:33:11,060 --> 00:33:12,660
I wouldn't even bother telling you this.

641
00:33:13,660 --> 00:33:14,500
My son.

642
00:33:14,820 --> 00:33:16,100
There's hope now.

643
00:33:16,340 --> 00:33:18,360
The Grand Princess sent a carriage
to pick you up.

644
00:33:18,500 --> 00:33:20,100
Her mansion has imperial physicians.

645
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:21,620
They'll surely heal your leg.

646
00:33:21,780 --> 00:33:22,980
That's great, Mother.

647
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:24,780
Let's go.

648
00:33:25,780 --> 00:33:26,820
Why are you standing there?

649
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:28,260
Come here and help.

650
00:33:28,260 --> 00:33:29,140
He can't go.

651
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:30,660
What did you say?

652
00:33:31,260 --> 00:33:32,820
