658
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:49,900
the other was General Cui's nephew.

659
00:33:50,220 --> 00:33:51,380
The one who's missing is

660
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,180
Rite Censor Sun's grandson.

661
