What do you mean by that?

665
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:01,980
My son is also an heir.

666
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:03,540
He's also a noble.

667
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:05,260
Stop deceiving yourself.

668
00:34:05,940 --> 00:34:07,740
Our family is declining now.

669
00:34:08,340 --> 00:34:09,700
With this incident,

670
00:34:10,860 --> 00:34:12,700
