671
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:18,060
The Censorate and the Rites Office

672
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:20,300
aren't easy to deal with.

673
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:22,380
They wouldn't let their kids

674
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:23,540
die in vain.

675
00:34:24,340 --> 00:34:25,500
If someone has to take

676
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:27,180
the blame for this,

677
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:28,660
who do you think

678
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:30,620
the Grand Princess will push forward

679
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:31,980
to take the fall?

680
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:36,100
Right, the Grand Princess

681
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,500
probably isn't so kind.

682
00:34:40,300 --> 00:34:41,140
So, what do you think

683
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:42,580
we should do now?

684
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:43,860
In any case,

685
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:46,260
