to the Grand Princess's Mansion.

686
00:34:48,620 --> 00:34:51,020
Please go and tell the Grand Princess

687
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:53,060
that Chongyi can't move

688
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:54,860
because of his leg.

689
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,780
Good.

690
00:34:57,700 --> 00:34:59,220
I'll go and tell her.

691
00:35:02,420 --> 00:35:03,980
I didn't expect you

692
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:07,060
to have some conscience.

693
00:35:07,820 --> 00:35:08,980
I'm not doing this for you

694
00:35:09,620 --> 00:35:11,100
but for my baby.

695
00:35:19,580 --> 00:35:20,580
What exactly caused

696
00:35:20,580 --> 00:35:21,900
the fire last night?

697
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:29,300
For the sake of our family,

698
00:35:29,940 --> 00:35:31,380
you should tell me the truth.

699
00:35:36,660 --> 00:35:37,780
Actually, last night,

700
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:40,860
besides the five of us,

701
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:45,780
