702
00:35:48,180 --> 00:35:49,500
They're searching for someone.

703
00:35:57,500 --> 00:35:58,940
They say many died.

704
00:36:03,300 --> 00:36:04,460
It's dangerous.

705
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:07,620
How is it? Any findings?

706
00:36:07,620 --> 00:36:08,460
No.

707
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:09,820
Long Dan,

708
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:11,620
go search over there.

709
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,620
