- Yes.

710
00:36:13,620 --> 00:36:16,060
Anyone who finds my grandson

711
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:18,300
will be rewarded 1,000 taels.

712
00:36:18,300 --> 00:36:19,580
1,000 taels.

713
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:21,180
It's 1,000 taels.

714
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,540
Yes, let's go find him.

715
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:23,500
Hurry up.

716
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:25,060
Over there, over there.

717
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:26,060
1,000 taels.

718
00:36:26,060 --> 00:36:27,100
- 1,000 taels.
- Mr. Sun.

719
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,500
This is the Jinshui River,

720
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,420
not a small creek.

721
00:36:29,580 --> 00:36:30,540
Even the best swimmer

722
00:36:30,540 --> 00:36:31,480
could have an accident.

723
00:36:33,020 --> 00:36:34,780
Please take back the reward.

724
00:36:34,780 --> 00:36:36,620
You can't find my grandson.

725
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,980
Can't I search myself?

726
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:41,460
The more people search,

727
00:36:41,660 --> 00:36:43,540
the greater the chance

728
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:44,700
of finding my grandson.

729
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:46,140
Over there.

730
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:47,540
- Look over there.
- Hurry.

731
00:36:47,540 --> 00:36:48,500
Go look.

732
00:36:49,820 --> 00:36:51,100
Master, Miss.

733
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:52,540
- How is it?
- Master, Miss.

734
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:53,540
Nothing there either.

735
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:02,180
No news is good news.

736
00:37:02,300 --> 00:37:03,420
It'll be fine.

737
00:37:03,780 --> 00:37:05,380
We'll definitely find your brother.

738
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:06,980
He's a troublemaker.

739
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:08,980
Troublemakers live long.

740
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:12,460
Someone's underwater.

741
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,100
My Lord, over here.

742
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:14,940
We found him.

743
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:16,620
We found him. Hurry.

744
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:20,300
Let's go, let's go.

745
00:37:20,420 --> 00:37:21,740
Let's go, Master.

746
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:23,620
Move, move.

747
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:24,620
Over here, over here.

748
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:26,540
Hurry. Over here.

749
00:37:26,540 --> 00:37:28,140
- Save him.
- Come and save him.

750
00:37:28,300 --> 00:37:29,140
Over there.

751
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:30,540
Master.

752
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:33,660
- Hurry and pull him up.
- Pull him up.

753
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,670
Hurry.

754
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,440
Get him up.

755
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:41,520
Got him.

756
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:42,580
It's really him.

757
00:37:42,580 --> 00:37:43,660
The purple robe...

758
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:48,660
Sheng loved purple robes the most.

759
00:37:50,140 --> 00:37:51,100
Sheng...

760
00:37:51,820 --> 00:37:54,420
How can you do this?

761
00:37:55,340 --> 00:37:58,420
How can you let your grandpa bury you?

762
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:00,380
- Chief.
- Miss.

763
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:01,220
Si.

764
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:03,780
- Miss.
- Send her back.

765
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:04,620
Yes.

766
00:38:20,180 --> 00:38:21,020
Miss,

767
00:38:22,100 --> 00:38:23,660
you haven't eaten anything all day.

768
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,100
At least drink some hot soup.

769
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:28,340
Aman,

770
00:38:30,180 --> 00:38:31,540
any news about my brother?

771
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:44,580
It's all my fault.

772
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:49,060
It's my fault.

773
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:17,500
Uncle,

774
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:20,140
why not go back and rest?

775
00:39:20,380 --> 00:39:21,300
I'll stay here.

776
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:24,060
Why is the Jinshui River

777
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:27,220
so deep

778
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:30,500
and so long?

779
00:39:32,180 --> 00:39:34,220
You can't overexert yourself.

780
00:39:34,700 --> 00:39:36,420
