783
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:51,300
Sure.

784
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:53,960
He'll certainly be alive.

785
00:40:03,100 --> 00:40:03,940
I...

786
00:40:06,420 --> 00:40:08,380
I'm not worthy to be a father.

787
00:40:10,860 --> 00:40:11,940
Since he was young,

788
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:15,300
I've never disciplined him.

789
00:40:16,460 --> 00:40:18,020
When he grew up,

790
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,220
all I did was scold him

791
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:25,100
and complain.

792
00:40:26,700 --> 00:40:28,900
I never truly cared about him.

793
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:33,100
Though he was mischievous,

794
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:36,620
he was a good kid.

795
00:40:42,100 --> 00:40:45,860
I failed him.

796
00:40:55,220 --> 00:40:56,140
Uncle, don't worry.

797
00:40:57,220 --> 00:40:58,580
I will definitely find him.

798
00:41:03,500 --> 00:41:05,140
We'll definitely find him.

799
00:41:05,140 --> 00:41:05,980
Yes.

800
00:41:09,020 --> 00:41:12,100
We'll definitely find him.

801
00:41:19,060 --> 00:41:19,980
Your Highness,

802
00:41:20,580 --> 00:41:22,460
you must help me.

803
00:41:22,460 --> 00:41:23,300
Your Highness,

804
00:41:24,020 --> 00:41:25,300
my son was burned.

805
00:41:25,580 --> 00:41:27,420
His face is unrecognizable.

806
00:41:27,580 --> 00:41:30,740
This is horrible, Your Highness.

807
00:41:33,020 --> 00:41:34,300
Mr. Zhang, sorry for your loss.

808
00:41:35,180 --> 00:41:36,660
But I don't understand

809
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:38,900
why your son

810
00:41:39,580 --> 00:41:40,540
was

811
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:41,900
with Princess Mingyue.

812
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:45,500
Your Highness, please trust me.

813
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:49,220
You're the reason why I'm here today.

814
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:51,060
And I am

815
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:53,220
loyal to you.

816
00:41:54,580 --> 00:41:55,460
Zhang Sheng

817
00:41:55,940 --> 00:41:57,620
was only my concubine's son.

818
00:41:58,020 --> 00:41:59,660
He was uneducated

819
00:41:59,940 --> 00:42:01,020
and unambitious,

820
00:42:01,380 --> 00:42:03,940
