821
00:42:05,220 --> 00:42:07,540
I also neglected to discipline him.

822
00:42:08,220 --> 00:42:10,260
I have no idea how this rascal

823
00:42:10,860 --> 00:42:12,180
got involved

824
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:13,860
with Princess Mingyue.

825
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:20,980
Though his mother was a concubine,

826
00:42:21,780 --> 00:42:23,740
