830
00:42:32,020 --> 00:42:32,860
Your Highness,

831
00:42:33,700 --> 00:42:35,860
it's the Grand Princess's fault
for bad parenting.

832
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:38,460
Princess Mingyue is undisciplined,

833
00:42:38,660 --> 00:42:40,940
indulging in pleasures
and losing herself,

834
00:42:41,300 --> 00:42:42,860
which has led to the accident

835
00:42:43,100 --> 00:42:45,260
and killed several men.

836
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:46,980
Your Highness,

837
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:49,540
I'll report it to His Majesty

838
00:42:49,980 --> 00:42:51,980
